snippet.textDisplay: Can I say Thank you for your playlist. I discovered this and was timely because I have trouble staying relaxed and want my heart to learn to calm down. I always overthink and think ahead, sometimes I forgot to slow down and reflect. These songs are what I needed to know that I still got time and can still do something about the present. God bless everyone who is reading this. To those who are tired, physically, emotionally, and mentally and want to find peace üòä.
